  m_Name: Chap1_4
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::LevelStoryData
  levelName: "m\xE0n 4"
  introLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "\u0111\xE3 g\u1EA7n 2 th\xE1ng tr\xF4i qua r\u1ED3i, t\u1EA1i sao l\u0169
      kinh t\u1EDFm n\xE0y c\u1EE9  xu\u1EA5t hi\u1EC7n m\xE3i th\u1EBF. C\xE1c th\xFA
      v\u1EADt trong r\u1EEBng \u0111\u1EC1u b\u1ECB ch\xFAng l\xE0m bi\u1EBFn m\u1EA5t
      c\u1EA3 r\u1ED3i  ch\u1EBFt ti\u1EC7t\u2026 L\u01B0\u01A1ng th\u1EF1c c\u0169ng
      s\u1EAFp c\u1EA1n ki\u1EC7t r\u1ED3i\u2026"
  - speaker: Shadow
    text: "g\xE2u g\xE2u !"
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "\u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c  r\u1ED3i shadow ch\xFAng l\u1EA1i t\u1EDBi n\u1EEFa
      r\u1ED3i!!"
  outroLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng c\u0169ng xong\u2026 Shadow \xE0\u2026 mi c\xF3 th\u1EC3
      c\xF9ng ta \u1EDF \u0111\xE2y ch\u1EDD th\xEAm v\xE0i ng\xE0y n\u1EEFa \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
      kh\xF4ng\u2026. Ta ngh\u0129 m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi s\u1EAFp v\u1EC1 t\u1EDBi
      r\u1ED3i\u2026"
  - speaker: Shadow
    text: "g\xE2u g\xE2u !"
